{{stack begin}}
{{Parent monthly clean up category|Unreferenced|Sources, Lacking|shortcut=CAT:ALS|shortcut2=WP:ALS|shortcut3=CAT:UNREF}}
Wikipedia articles that have '''no''' [[Wikipedia:Citing sources|citations]] belong in this category.

'''Please help improve an article in this category by adding [[WP:REFB|references]] to [[WP:Reliable sources|reliable sources]] that [[Wikipedia:Verifiability|verify]] content within the article. This category is for <mark>completely unsourced</mark> articles.  Once one (1) URL or other reliable source has been added anywhere on the page, the {{tl|unreferenced}} tag should be removed.  See [[Template:Unreferenced/doc|the template's documentation]] for more information.'''

{{align|center|{{Clickable button 2|Special:RandomInCategory/All articles lacking sources|{{large|Fix a random page lacking sources}}|class=mw-ui-progressive}}|style=margin:1em}}

{{align|center|{{resbox|'''{{large|{{Random page in category|text=Browse a random subcategory of this one}}}}'''}}|style=margin:1em}}

{{Filter category by topic|All articles lacking sources‎}}

See also:
* [[:Category:Articles lacking reliable references]] for weakly sourced articles with the templates {{tl|Primary sources}} and {{tl|Unreliable source?}}
* [[:Category:Articles needing additional references]] for partially sourced articles with the template {{tl|More citations needed}} or {{tl|One source}}
* [[:Category:Articles with unsourced statements]] for articles with small numbers of statements lacking references, identified by {{tl|Citation needed}} or {{tl|Failed verification}}
* [[:Category:All articles lacking sources]] for all pages marked as needing references by {{tl|Unreferenced}}, sorted alphabetically.

You can also participate in [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Unreferenced articles]] or [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Reliability]].

This [[Wikipedia:Categorization|category]] subdivides based on when references were requested. An [[Wikipedia:WikiProject_Unreferenced_articles/Historical_data|archive]] of the historical sizes of each monthly subcategory is maintained by WikiProject Unreferenced articles. 

;See also
* [[Wikipedia:Template index/Sources of articles]]
{{stack end}}

